{"tid":1511072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[知己知彼]The First Law of Pikayung話咗畀我地知呢場運動嘅關鍵","createTime":"2019-08-27T11:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T13:19:51.000Z","uid":40170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50bcf006c87292e68c9dfeee7e9028fd58127c99","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"Pikachu係比卡起就大家都識啦<br />\nPikayung你又聽過未呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>The First Law of Pikayung 畀家用第一定律</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n第一次畀家用嚟講 <br />\n其實只靠一個原則去決定畀幾多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>家用只可以加 可以hold <br />\n但唔可以少過上一個月嘅家用</ins></strong></span><br />\n少咗會問長問短 屋企以為自己好唔掂<br />\n甚至萌生一種不孝嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n我地睇睇兩個case<br />\n<br />\nCase I<br />\n第一個月 1000<br />\n第二個月 1000<br />\n...<br />\n第十二個月 1000<br />\n<br />\n一年共12000<br />\n<br />\nCase II<br />\n第一個月 200<br />\n第二個月 200<br />\n第三個月 400<br />\n第四個月 400<br />\n第五個月 600<br />\n第六個月 600<br />\n...<br />\n第十二個月 1200<br />\n<br />\n一年共8400<br />\n<br />\nCase II嘅感覺無論點都畀case I感覺好好多<br />\n仲好似越撈越掂 而且就算你第十一個月開始以後都只係畀1000<br />\n屋企都會覺得你人工又無乜加 家用keep到都ok啦<br />\n其實計point 逐年加人工嘅概念我都懷疑係參考 The First Law of Pikayung<br />\n<br />\n重點喺邊？<br />\n無錯！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係家用破處嘅價錢有幾多！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另一個要留意嘅地方係提高家用嘅時間係隨時可以停<br />\n因為根據條Law 家用可以加 可以hold但唔可以跌<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n運用呢條Law嘅時候要留意<br />\n隨咗要喺畀嘅一方諗 <br />\n仲要喺收嘅一方諗<br />\n目標係maximize我地自己嘅收獲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n換言之 我地有幾件事要留意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一。要破處！要家用破處！</strong></span><br />\n點解班狗一定要幾十人捉一個手足呢？<br />\n點解班狗要用幾百警力幫一架被圍嘅車走呢？<br />\n點解班狗一有人落單就會派幾百人去救嘅？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為有第一個 就會有二三四五六個！！ </span> </span><br />\n簡單啲講<br />\n人數許可嘅時候搶犯要做 仲要快<br />\n圍堵係完全無用！！！！！<br />\n你二萬人叫黑警都唔會放個手足！！！！！<br />\n係 係好難 但只要有第一次<br />\n佢地處都破嘅 我方士氣提升之餘仲可以挫佢銳氣！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">二。寧化飛灰，不作浮塵！！！！</span></strong><br />\n抗爭者一方而言<br />\n我地一係all or nothing<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定唔可以接受政府唧牙膏式嘅回應</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為五大訴求係缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n一接受咗less evil 嘅方案<br />\n一接受咗一兩個政府嘅回應<br />\n佢隨時會停！！！！<br />\n而且每接受一個訴求都要付出一啲民意！！！<br />\n<strong><ins>更甚係林鄭條友會反口！！！！！！</ins></strong><br />\n詳情參閱皇后碼頭保衛戰 喜帖街保衛戰<br />\n<br />\n另一方面 我地要適時upgrade訴求<br />\n詳情參閱各大銀行嘅min pay政策<br />\n留意第一個月無還錢 第二個月淨係還第一個月min pay會發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問心 獨立調查狗隊 你接受咩？</span></strong><br />\n對唔對得住被凌辱嘅絲打？<br />\n對唔對得住我地已經畀咗出去嘅三隻眼 六條命？<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 First Law都適用抗爭破處嘅朋友<br />\n記住<br />\n<strong>Step 1: Gear up!! <br />\nStep 2: Gear a friend up!!<br />\nStep 3: Repeat step 2.</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>發過夢 佢就會搵到自己嘅位置</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n政府好明白呢條Law <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且仲用好多唔係回應嘅行為冒充回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足一定要gear up 企硬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n解散狗隊，匡正我城！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c9e6a21e647582492a8aacafd65268992d406ce","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"Pish!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6efaadd3da244a12c3c5ee4f1f4b107c1103af","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"推你老母十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831劍指匪國<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿通匪類</span></span>"},{"pid":"5922d82b71987d2196fb5d068c61df9ee6e60dad","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"Pish呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f91f36aa147e8afeaebc25afbeb881c44bae9d5","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"再推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f17aa981edf1b084f9f43ce253cf68741502920","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831 西環見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906cf2b7c0d492d42e104d940303a25292338e5","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">91揸春袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"c382a29afb3bca54a0ea6119957a0f712be99140","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"9月只做一件事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揸你老母個春袋</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再揸埋你春袋個老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f46f61dc06618ec3596d40910ea817c8041af4e","tid":1511072,"uid":47392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:05:33.000Z","msg":"真心講如果佢承認政權不合法並解散政府<br />\n再即刻雙普選<br />\n我唔介意等民選政府搞嗰四大訴求<br />\n<br />\n雖然無乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bca1d3b3d86606799e7409c77ccb096874bd93","tid":1511072,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"fo